ds food when you have precious babies??</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TIsY3K0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sure, it looks delicious. But I’m not even hungry. But she made me make it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sUMhwS1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’ll eat when I need to. Right now, I need to snuggle with the babies. The soup will be there. I am having too much fun! Thank you, bestie, but I’m good. Big yawn!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/XSh4exW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KittensForDays]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>20% of the top earners are doing 80% of consumption, which is why the economy looks better than it feels for 80% of us. The stock market is not the economy, and this trick is AWESOME!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4aHbpDI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7q17678.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4aHbpDI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[unclefishbits]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's meant to be!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/bcBBsnL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nIFIWoB.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sauces: https://www.youtube.com/@dev_lemons</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/bcBBsnL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SirReginaldTheThirteenth]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>There's weird. And then there's Weird.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/cAj0pXU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lMo6tYB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He'll never match those UHF vibes.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/cAj0pXU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Bandlith]]></dc:crea