div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/69ANDkD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LxGu05a.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Act 1 spoilers in a few pics!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TABFIzy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Last warning - spoilers are below!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2ZjsPnC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>These are my favorite shots but I have to bury them - I know the game has been out for almost a year but I still want to warn people!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hxpRuYe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ABpTvE8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tpDnwgo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LittleLuckyCosplay]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>We have contractions!!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gLRJWPX</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/62xRFF3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gLRJWPX</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KittensForDays]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>“When we say restaurants in Ukraine are dog-friendly, we mean it — all dogs, even those that might be confused for bear.” - Richard Woodruff.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/llNw0XA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bcsxWKh.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/llNw0XA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vladrichdemaclant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Here we go again, the Gestapo at San Francisco airport.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XlA9h5q</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Jvs3hzs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Didn’t have this problem when Biden was in office!
Trump is doing a really good job diverting attention from the Epstein files.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9MOgERf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>TSA is largely funded by a tax on every ticket. It adds $5.60 to every one-way ticket & $11.20 to roundtrips. Everyone in line right now is already paying the TSA fee, even for free reward travel. The government has previously diverted that money to the Treasury. Pay the agents.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/XlA9h5q</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LunaAtlas]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>67 no thanks</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JwLbXJU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tiGl3L6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#memes #random #jokes #climbing #latticeclimbing</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JwLbXJU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Climber4x4]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Dragons Daughter</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/gOnBXqJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uuvFzXC.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Source 

https://www.instagram.com/reel/DWGmD45kttJ/?igsh=djJnMHNja3l0OWN0</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/gOnBXqJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[77thtimesthecharm]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>We’re kinda sorta thinking about maybe getting close to kittens</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Y8OAKor</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5l1hiVL.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I came home at lunch to feed my pregnant foster mama cat Bobbie and I noticed a little leakage coming from her. She’s very restless, keeps trying to groom (her belly is too big for her to reach!), keeps meowing at me and using the litter box constantly, and isn’t eating as much. She’s been doing this type of thing for days so it doesn’t really mean anything, but the goop coming out of her IS new. My supervisor is letting me telework the rest of today so I’ll be here one way or another! (Edit: a bunch of you have asked what probiotics I give Bobbie, and it’s FortiFlora for felines)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Y8OAKor</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KittensForDays]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Mama needed a little help</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/fxLx3q1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TNzXxr2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bobbie seems a little overwhelmed and ran off with number one so I’ll do my part and help out number two. Gonna put her with mama now</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/fxLx3q1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[KittensForDays]]></dc:creator></item><item><title></title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7PiGBN5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IK90JZM.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/7PiGBN5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[NooPogodi]]><